snippet.title: RC Simulation 2.0 Is now FULL RELEASE! Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Drive all kinds of RC Cars, Boats, Rock Crawlers, Planes or Quadcopters on any of the 250+ Workshop Tracks. The game includes an in-game Track Editor and Vehicle Painter to create tons of scenarios and Paint schemes. RC Sim is made by a solo developer and still is in development.
RC Simulation 2.0 Is now FULL RELEASE! Gameplay Trailer
